'''Niki Botelho''' portrayed [[Teek (Teek)|Teek]] in the [[1985]] made-for-TV film ''[[Ewoks: The Battle for Endor]]''. She returned to the ''[[Star Wars]]'' universe to play a [[Jawa]] in ''[[Star Wars: The Mandalorian]]''<ref name="TalkingBay">{{WebCite|url=https://talkingbay94.libsyn.com/niki-botelho-bringing-teek-to-life-in-ewoks-the-battle-for-endor|text=Niki Botelho: Teek in Ewoks - The Battle for Endor|date=2020-09-23|archivedate=20230605073433}}</ref> and a [[power droid]] in ''[[Star Wars: Ahsoka]]'', where she was credited as "Nicole Botelho."<ref name="Ahsoka1">{{Ahsoka|Part One: Master and Apprentice}}</ref><ref name="Ahsoka4">{{Ahsoka|Part Four: Fallen Jedi}}</ref>

